{"id":212830,"type":4,"name":"PLAYERUNKNOWN'S BATTLEGROUNDS","name_cn":"绝地求生","date":"2017-12-20","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/0f/30/212830_JDbPZ.jpg","rating":{"rank":6979,"total":446,"count":{"1":14,"2":12,"3":16,"4":26,"5":77,"6":144,"7":104,"8":40,"9":11,"10":2},"score":5.8},"summary":"绝地求生(PLAYERUNKNOWN’S BATTLEGROUNDS)是大逃杀类型的游戏，每一局游戏将有100名玩家参与，他们将被投放在绝地岛(battlegrounds)的上空，游戏开始跳伞时所有人都一无所有。\r\n\r\n游戏展开的方式是：玩家赤手空拳地分布在岛屿的各个角落，利用岛上多样的武器与道具。随着时间的流逝，岛上的安全地带越来越少，特定地区也会发生爆炸的情况，最终只有一人存活获得胜利。游戏的每一局比赛都会随机转换安全区，这样玩家的很新鲜与紧张感会更加强烈。\r\n\r\nPLAYERUNKNOWN (Brendan Greene – 目前为Bluehole Creative Director )是大逃杀类游戏的开拓者。他在ARMA2初次展现大逃杀模式，他的大逃杀模式成为ARMA系列与H1Z1:King of the Kill的基础。现在， 他为了开发真正的大逃杀游戏而在蓝洞(Bluehole)开发绝地求生(PLAYERUNKNOWN’S BATTLEGROUNDS)。\r\n\r\nNOT JUST A GAME, THIS IS BATTLE ROYALE。\r\n(这不仅是游戏，是大逃杀。) ","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>绝地求生</li><li><span>开发: </span><a href=\"/person/31694\">PUBG Corporation</a></li><li><span>发行: </span><a href=\"/person/31693\">Krafton</a>、<a href=\"/person/43209\">Kakao Games</a>（PC/PS4/Stadia）、<a href=\"/person/18886\">腾讯游戏</a>（中国大陆）、<a href=\"/person/16859\">Xbox Game Studios</a>、智凡迪（<a href=\"/person/33926\">智冠科技</a>）（港澳台）</li><li><span>游戏设计师: </span><a href=\"/person/36477\">Brendan Greene</a></li><li><span>导演: </span><a href=\"/person/36477\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">Brendan Greene</a>、Tae-seok Jang</li><li><span>别名: </span>배틀그라운드</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>绝地求生：大逃杀</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>吃鸡</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>PUBG</li><li><span>平台: </span>Google Stadia</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PS4</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Xbox One</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PC</li><li><span>游戏类型: </span>射击</li><li><span>游戏引擎: </span>Unreal Engine 4</li><li><span>游玩人数: </span>100人</li><li><span>发行日期: </span>2017年12月20日</li><li><span>售价: </span>$29.99 / 98元→免费游玩</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>h